<div id="scroll-container" class="px-small transition-colors md:px-medium lg:px-large box-border">
    <nav class="z-10 flex flex-col justify-between pt-small md:pt-medium snap-center lg:pt-large box-border h-screen relative">
        <div>
            <p class="animate-in text-3xl mb-4 font-light">Hugo Sundberg</p>
            <h1 class="animate-in text-5xl xs:text-7xl font-bold md:text-8xl">Portfolio.</h1>
        </div>
        <ul>
            <li class="animate-in mb-4"><a class="bg-gradientDarkRed {{textGradientOnHover}} text-3xl font-bold" data-en="Projects" href="#projects">Projekt</a></li>
            <li class="animate-in mb-4"><a class="bg-gradientDarkBlue {{textGradientOnHover}} text-3xl font-bold" data-en="About me" href="#about-me">Om mig</a></li>
        </ul>
        <div class="animate-in flex items-center gap-1 mb-10">
            <img class="h-4" src="images/icons/lang.svg" alt="">
            <button id="language-switch" class="w-fit underline" data-en="Byt till svenska" href="">Switch to english</button>
        </div>
    </nav>
    {% set imageBaseStyle = "z-0 object-cover image lg:h-[55vh] h-[30vh] xs:h-[43vh] w-full max-w-[1024px]" %}
    {% set textCardBaseStyle = "z-10 text-sm md:text-base translate-y-[200px] backdrop-blur-lg shadow-card bg-white/80 relative p-card-small md:p-card-medium lg:p-card-large -mt-small md:-mt-medium lg:-mt-large w-full max-w-[580px] rounded-card-small md:rounded-card-medium bg-white shall-animate" %}
    {% set techContainerBaseStyle = "absolute top-[6px] md:top-[10px] flex gap-[10px]" %}
    {% set techImageBaseStyle = "h-full w-full shadow-card-small relative invisible xs:visible rounded-icon-small md:rounded-icon-medium object-cover" %}
    {% for project in projects %}
    {% set imageSrc = project.images[0].path %}
    <section {% if(loop.first) %} id="projects" {% endif %} class="relative mb-16 h-full snap-start w-full flex items-center">
        <div class="w-full h-full">
            {% if loop.index % 2 == 0 %}
        {# Image to right #}
                <div class="max-w-[1024px] ml-auto relative translate-x-small md:translate-x-medium lg:translate-x-large right-0 w-full">
                    <div class="{{techContainerBaseStyle}} left-[6px] md:left-[10px]">
                        {% for technnology in project.technnologies %}
                            <a class="show-child-p-on-hover h-8 w-8 small:h-14 small:w-14 md:h-16 md:w-16 hover:rotate-6 transition duration-300" href="{{technnology.url}}"><img class="{{techImageBaseStyle}}" src="{{technnology.path}}" alt="{{technnology.name}}"><p class="opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-300 whitespace-nowrap bg-white/80 shadow-card-small backdrop-blur-lg rounded-icon-smaller sm:rounded-icon-small md:rounded-icon-medium mt-1 w-fit px-2 py-[2px]">{{technnology.name}}</p></a> 
                        {% endfor %}
                    </div>
                    <img sizes="(max-width: 1080px) 80vw, 1024px" class="{{imageBaseStyle}} ml-auto rounded-image-small-right md:rounded-image-medium-right" srcset="{{imageSrc}}" alt="">
                </div>
                <div class="{{textCardBaseStyle}} ml-auto">
            {% else %} 
        {# Image to left #}
                 <div class="max-w-[1024px] relative -ml-small md:-ml-medium lg:-ml-large left-0 w-full">
                    <div class="{{techContainerBaseStyle}} right-[6px] md:right-[10px]">
                        {% for technnology in project.technnologies %}
                            <a class="show-child-p-on-hover h-8 w-8 small:h-14 small:w-14 md:h-16 md:w-16 hover:rotate-6 transition duration-300" href="{{technnology.url}}"><img class="{{techImageBaseStyle}}" src="{{technnology.path}}" alt="{{technnology.name}}"><p class="opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-300 whitespace-nowrap bg-white/80 shadow-card-small backdrop-blur-lg rounded-icon-smaller sm:rounded-icon-small md:rounded-icon-medium mt-1 w-fit px-2 py-[2px]">{{technnology.name}}</p></a> 
                        {% endfor %}
                    </div>
                    <img sizes="(max-width: 1080px) 80vw, 1024px" class="{{imageBaseStyle}} rounded-image-small md:rounded-image-medium" srcset="{{imageSrc}}" alt="">
                </div>
                <div class="{{textCardBaseStyle}}">
            {% endif %}
                <h2 class="text-3xl mb-5 font-bold" data-en="{{project.title.en}}">{{project.title.sv}}</h2>
                <p class="mb-3" data-en="{{project.description.en}}">{{project.description.sv}}</p>
                {% if(project.site) %}
                <div class="flex gap-3 mb-3">
                    <img class="w-6" src="images/icons/site-icon.svg" alt="">
                    <a target="_blank" class="bg-gradientDarkRed {{textGradientOnHover}} underline" href="{{project.site}}" data-en="Visit the site">Besök sidan</a>
                </div>
                {% endif %}
                {% if(project.github) %}
                <div class="flex gap-3 mb-3">
                    <img class="w-6" src="images/icons/gh-icon.svg" alt="">
                    {% if(project.site) %}
                    <a target="_blank" class="bg-gradientDarkBlue {{textGradientOnHover}} underline" href="{{project.github}}" data-en="Or check out the github repository" >Eller kolla in repot på github</a>
                    {% else %}
                    <a target="_blank" class="bg-gradientDarkBlue {{textGradientOnHover}} underline" href="{{project.github}}" data-en="Check out the github repository" >Kolla in repot på github</a>
                    {% endif %}
                </div>
                {% endif %}
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    {% endfor %}
    <section id="about-me" class="flex mb-small md:mb-medium flex-col gap-0 md:gap-4 aboutMeBreak:items-center justify-center">
        <div class="flex-col-reverse aboutMeBreak:flex-row flex gap-5 md:gap-8">
            <img class="max-w-[366px] object-cover rounded-card-small md:rounded-card-medium shadow-card-small h-[30vh] xs:h-[35vh] md:h-[40vh]" srcset="images/aboutme/FullSizeRender_center_norsv9_c_scale,w_80.jpg 80w,images/aboutme/FullSizeRender_center_norsv9_c_scale,w_663.jpg 663w,images/aboutme/FullSizeRender_center_norsv9_c_scale,w_862.jpg 862w,images/aboutme/FullSizeRender_center_norsv9_c_scale,w_1034.jpg 1034w,images/aboutme/FullSizeRender_center_norsv9_c_scale,w_1040.jpg 1040w" sizes="(max-width: 450px) calc(100vw - 64px), 366px" alt="">
            <h2 class="text-6xl sm:text-7xl md:text-8xl font-bold mt-4 mb-4" data-en="About me.">Om mig.</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="text-sm md:text-base relative pr-small md:pr-medium">
            <div class="-mt-small left-small backdrop-blur-lg shadow-card bg-white/80 relative p-card-small md:p-card-medium lg:p-card-large w-full max-w-[580px] rounded-card-small md:rounded-card-medium bg-white shall-animate">
                <h3 class="text-4xl mb-card-small md:mb-card-medium lg:mb-card-large">Hugo Sundberg</h3>
                <p data-en="I am a 26-year-old web developer who works at Itiden in Gothenburg. I recently graduated from the Web Developer course at Yrgo and have previously studied and worked as a production manager. After a few years in the IT and web sphere, I can't see myself working in any other industry. When I'm not programming, I like to work out or play disc golf. I have a great interest in design and UX and believe that good design and UX are a must for good functionality to be able to deliver value. Programming is my hobby and passion." class="mb-5 md:mb-7">Jag är en 26-årig webbutvecklare på som arbetar på Itiden i Göteborg. Jag tog nyligen examen från utbildningen Webbutvecklare på Yrgo och har tidigare studerat och arbetat som produktionsledare. Efter några år inom IT- och webbsfären så kan jag inte se mig arbeta inom någon annan bransch. När jag inte programmerar så gillar jag att träna eller spela disc-golf. Jag har ett stort intresse för design och UX och anser att bra design och UX är ett måste för att bra funktionalitet ska kunna leverera värde. Programmering är min hobby och passion.</p>
                <div class="flex gap-3 mb-3">
                    <img class="w-6" src="images/icons/gh-icon.svg" alt="">
                    <a target="_blank" class="bg-gradientDarkBlue {{textGradientOnHover}} underline" href="https://github.com/Hugocsundberg" data-en="Check out my github for more projects">Kolla in min github för fler projekt</a>
                </div>
                <div class="flex gap-3 mb-3">
                    <img class="w-6" src="images/icons/linkedin.svg" alt="">
                    <a target="_blank" class="bg-gradientDarkRed {{textGradientOnHover}} underline" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/hugosundberg/" data-en="My linkedIn profile" >Min LinkedIn profil</a>
                </div>
                <div class="flex gap-3 mb-3">
                    <img class="w-6" src="images/icons/document.svg" alt="">
                    <a target="_blank" class="bg-gradientDarkBlue {{textGradientOnHover}} underline" href="https://hugosundbergcv.netlify.app/?lang" data-en="Resume">CV</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>